1
00:01:11,480 --> 00:01:13,640
Yu Na answered all the questions fluently.

2
00:01:13,640 --> 00:01:14,840
Don't you think it's a bit strange?

3
00:01:14,840 --> 00:01:15,320
Yes.

4
00:01:15,920 --> 00:01:16,960
Have someone keep an eye on her.

5
00:01:16,960 --> 00:01:18,220
I already told them to.

6
00:01:20,400 --> 00:01:21,320
And what about Xia Lin?

7
00:01:21,320 --> 00:01:22,000
Are we going?

8
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:23,200
Let's go. I'll drive.

9
00:01:39,280 --> 00:01:40,340
Please have a seat.

10
00:01:40,920 --> 00:01:41,780
Hello, Ms. Xia.

11
00:01:42,039 --> 00:01:42,840
I'm Jiang Mei.

12
00:01:43,320 --> 00:01:43,720
Hello.

13
00:01:43,960 --> 00:01:44,960
I'd like to ask you

14
00:01:45,320 --> 00:01:46,580
if you know Tian Liang.

15
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:48,759
I do.

16
00:01:49,920 --> 00:01:50,720
What's wrong?

17
00:01:51,360 --> 00:01:51,890
Nothing.

18
00:01:52,240 --> 00:01:54,100
I just want to know how you two met,

19
00:01:54,520 --> 00:01:56,250
and what your relationship is.

20
00:01:57,720 --> 00:01:58,200
I...

21
00:01:58,400 --> 00:01:59,729
He's a trainer at my gym.

22
00:02:00,040 --> 00:02:00,680
That's it.

23
00:02:01,760 --> 00:02:02,160
I see.

24
00:02:02,680 --> 00:02:03,480
Because we found out

25
00:02:03,480 --> 00:02:06,210
that you called each other 14 times within a week.

26
00:02:08,199 --> 00:02:09,639
When I was working out before,

27
00:02:09,639 --> 00:02:10,400
I sprained my waist.

28
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:12,060
So I called him to ask about it.

29
00:02:12,360 --> 00:02:13,680
You consulted him so frequently.

30
00:02:13,680 --> 00:02:15,140
Did you go there every day?

31
00:02:15,600 --> 00:02:16,040
No.

32
00:02:16,400 --> 00:02:18,400
I probably only go a few times a week.

33
00:02:20,480 --> 00:02:21,210
Understood.

34
00:02:21,400 --> 00:02:23,329
Have you seen Tian Liang recently?

35
00:02:23,920 --> 00:02:24,280
No.

36
00:02:24,960 --> 00:02:27,420
What were you doing on the night of July 25th?

37
00:02:29,320 --> 00:02:30,640
July 25th?

38
00:02:31,560 --> 00:02:32,890
I was at home that night.

39
00:02:33,400 --> 00:02:35,200
You didn't go to Dahei Mountain?

40
00:02:35,400 --> 00:02:36,329
Dahei Mountain?

41
00:02:37,160 --> 00:02:38,400
No, I've never been there.

42
00:02:38,400 --> 00:02:39,720
I have classes at school during the day,

43
00:02:39,720 --> 00:02:40,920
and I go home at night.

44
00:02:41,560 --> 00:02:42,600
What happened to Tian Liang?

45
00:02:42,600 --> 00:02:43,240
Ms. Xia,

46
00:02:45,320 --> 00:02:47,120
did Tian Liang have any enemies?

47
00:02:48,960 --> 00:02:50,160
How would I know that?

48
00:02:50,440 --> 00:02:52,400
Besides being a fitness trainer,

49
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:54,079
did he have any other jobs

50
00:02:54,079 --> 00:02:55,610
or other sources of income?

51
00:02:58,079 --> 00:02:58,840
I'm not sure.

52
00:03:00,640 --> 00:03:02,480
What exactly happened to him?

53
00:03:03,400 --> 00:03:05,660
It's inconvenient to tell you right now.

54
00:03:05,880 --> 00:03:06,920
Captain Jiang just came today

55
00:03:06,920 --> 00:03:08,000
to ask a few questions.

56
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:10,330
Call me directly if you think of anything.

57
00:03:10,360 --> 00:03:11,560
We'll take our leave.

58
00:03:11,560 --> 00:03:12,000
Okay.

59
00:03:12,640 --> 00:03:14,160
Sorry for the intrusion today, Mr. Xia.

60
00:03:14,160 --> 00:03:14,560
It's fine.

61
00:03:14,560 --> 00:03:15,320
Really sorry about it.

62
00:03:15,320 --> 00:03:15,920
Thank you.

63
00:03:16,480 --> 00:03:17,079
Shen Feng.

64
00:03:17,800 --> 00:03:18,960
In a few days, Song Qing...

65
00:03:18,960 --> 00:03:19,620
I remember.

66
00:03:21,040 --> 00:03:21,900
I'll go see her.

67
00:03:22,600 --> 00:03:23,130
Goodbye.

68
00:03:25,640 --> 00:03:26,170
Goodbye.

69
00:03:26,320 --> 00:03:27,380
I won't see you out.

70
00:03:35,880 --> 00:03:37,410
You knew each other before?

71
00:03:42,400 --> 00:03:44,730
What kind of person do you think Xia Lin is?

72
00:03:45,200 --> 00:03:45,960
Ms. Xia,

73
00:03:46,480 --> 00:03:48,079
she is a model for our school,

74
00:03:48,520 --> 00:03:50,200
the only one with a senior professional title.

75
00:03:50,200 --> 00:03:50,800
Is that so?

76
00:03:51,520 --> 00:03:52,480
Has Ms. Xia

77
00:03:52,600 --> 00:03:54,200
been acting unusual lately?

78
00:03:55,160 --> 00:03:55,720
No.

79
00:03:58,760 --> 00:03:59,620
Thank you, sir.

80
00:04:08,920 --> 00:04:11,250
I could tell Xia Lin was acting unnatural.

81
00:04:11,480 --> 00:04:12,640
But I'm not sure

82
00:04:12,800 --> 00:04:14,920
if it's just her instinctive reaction to seeing the police

83
00:04:14,920 --> 00:04:16,920
or if she's really involved in this.

84
00:04:18,279 --> 00:04:20,800
Ms. Xia seemed quite calm,

85
00:04:21,480 --> 00:04:23,280
but her eyes were a bit evasive.

86
00:04:25,600 --> 00:04:27,400
Did you scare her?

87
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:28,760
Me?

88
00:04:31,240 --> 00:04:33,360
Don't I look kind and friendly?

89
00:04:38,560 --> 00:04:40,240
You and Ms. Xia,

90
00:04:40,840 --> 00:04:41,840
are you two close?

91
00:04:43,440 --> 00:04:44,440
Not really.

92
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:46,860
We don't contact each other much.

93
00:04:48,000 --> 00:04:50,330
But we've known each other for a few years.

94
00:04:51,600 --> 00:04:53,920
The frequency of Xia Lin and Tian Liang's phone calls

95
00:04:53,920 --> 00:04:55,280
and their

96
00:04:55,280 --> 00:04:56,000
chatting frequency on social media

97
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:58,000
are completely disproportionate.

98
00:04:58,000 --> 00:04:58,520
Indeed.

99
00:04:59,040 --> 00:05:01,040
Normally, with this frequency of contact,

100
00:05:01,040 --> 00:05:02,500
their social media traces

101
00:05:02,600 --> 00:05:03,920
wouldn't be so clean.

102
00:05:05,720 --> 00:05:06,640
Unless...

103
00:05:08,320 --> 00:05:10,180
they were deliberately deleted.

104
00:06:11,000 --> 00:06:13,120
According to surveillance and alibis,

105
00:06:13,120 --> 00:06:14,240
Yu Na and Xia Lin haven't been to

106
00:06:14,240 --> 00:06:16,040
Dahei Mountain over the past two days.

107
00:06:16,040 --> 00:06:17,400
Xia Lin only traveled between school and home.

108
00:06:17,400 --> 00:06:19,000
She didn't even go to the gym.

109
00:06:19,760 --> 00:06:22,480
Yu Na also only traveled between home and her company.

110
00:06:22,480 --> 00:06:24,760
They didn't have the time to commit the crime.

111
00:06:24,760 --> 00:06:26,160
Although we haven't made any new discoveries

112
00:06:26,160 --> 00:06:27,640
regarding their whereabouts,

113
00:06:27,640 --> 00:06:29,160
but within a week, Xia Lin

114
00:06:29,160 --> 00:06:30,880
called Tian Liang 14 times.

115
00:06:31,520 --> 00:06:32,640
But if you check his text messages,

116
00:06:32,640 --> 00:06:33,480
there are only a few words.

117
00:06:33,480 --> 00:06:34,280
It's so weird.

118
00:06:34,800 --> 00:06:36,240
So whether they are just

119
00:06:36,280 --> 00:06:37,810
a normal coach and trainee,

120
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:39,400
we still have to confirm.

121
00:06:40,040 --> 00:06:41,840
But Xia Lin didn't have the time to commit the crime.

122
00:06:41,840 --> 00:06:43,320
And she had no motive.

123
00:06:44,080 --> 00:06:46,409
From the cross section of the severed arm,

124
00:06:46,520 --> 00:06:48,159
the force of dismemberment was enormous.

125
00:06:48,159 --> 00:06:50,200
And judging from Tian Liang's build,

126
00:06:50,200 --> 00:06:52,860
whether it's dumping or dismembering the body,

127
00:06:53,080 --> 00:06:54,600
it's very unlikely to be a woman.

128
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:57,000
It's highly likely a man committed the crime.

129
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:57,730
In that case,

130
00:06:57,840 --> 00:06:59,840
let's investigate Tian Liang's social network

131
00:06:59,840 --> 00:07:01,880
and see who had the strongest motive to kill him.

132
00:07:01,880 --> 00:07:03,000
Tian Liang's social network

133
00:07:03,000 --> 00:07:04,120
seems complicated at first glance,

134
00:07:04,120 --> 00:07:05,720
but it's actually simple to sort out.

135
00:07:05,720 --> 00:07:06,920
His wife is Zhang Yan.

136
00:07:07,160 --> 00:07:08,720
His wife's lover is Li Wei.

137
00:07:09,120 --> 00:07:10,960
Besides that, the only other potential issue

138
00:07:10,960 --> 00:07:12,620
would be him and his students.

139
00:07:13,560 --> 00:07:16,640
So figuring out the relationship between Tian Liang and Xia Lin

140
00:07:16,640 --> 00:07:17,520
could be

141
00:07:18,000 --> 00:07:19,520
a big clue for solving the case.

142
00:07:19,520 --> 00:07:20,000
Right.

143
00:07:21,040 --> 00:07:22,440
Xia Lin works at a school,

144
00:07:22,840 --> 00:07:24,600
so her schedule is very regular.

145
00:07:24,600 --> 00:07:26,720
When she's working, Tian Liang doesn't have time.

146
00:07:26,720 --> 00:07:28,560
When Tian Liang is off work, she doesn't have time either.

147
00:07:28,560 --> 00:07:30,120
Even under such circumstances,

148
00:07:30,120 --> 00:07:32,780
the two of them were still in such close contact.

149
00:07:32,840 --> 00:07:35,040
They must have a special relationship.

150
00:07:40,480 --> 00:07:41,480
About Tian Liang,

151
00:07:41,600 --> 00:07:43,460
why would the police question me?

152
00:07:47,080 --> 00:07:47,680
I am so

153
00:07:48,240 --> 00:07:49,400
happy today.

154
00:07:54,320 --> 00:07:55,050
Are you okay?

155
00:08:01,400 --> 00:08:01,880
Honey.

156
00:08:04,760 --> 00:08:05,560
What's wrong?

157
00:08:06,840 --> 00:08:07,770
Why are you back?

158
00:08:08,360 --> 00:08:09,290
Are you alright?

159
00:08:09,840 --> 00:08:10,440
I

160
00:08:10,800 --> 00:08:11,560
am fine.

161
00:08:12,800 --> 00:08:14,330
I might be too tired lately.

162
00:08:14,840 --> 00:08:16,240
I'm feeling a bit unwell.

163
00:08:16,480 --> 00:08:17,880
You're not feeling well?

164
00:08:20,720 --> 00:08:21,480
I'm fine.

165
00:08:22,320 --> 00:08:23,320
Have you eaten?

166
00:08:23,480 --> 00:08:24,480
Let me get you something to eat.

167
00:08:24,480 --> 00:08:25,080
No need.

168
00:08:25,160 --> 00:08:25,760
You just

169
00:08:26,400 --> 00:08:26,920
rest.

170
00:08:28,120 --> 00:08:29,780
Then I'll go lie down for a bit.

171
00:08:35,440 --> 00:08:37,440
How about I take you to the hospital?

172
00:08:37,799 --> 00:08:38,320
No need.

173
00:08:38,679 --> 00:08:40,940
I'll be fine after lying down for a while.

174
00:09:32,600 --> 00:09:35,360
They say a plain wife and land close by are family treasures.

175
00:09:35,360 --> 00:09:36,960
But men still like to marry

176
00:09:37,080 --> 00:09:38,080
beautiful women.

177
00:09:38,480 --> 00:09:40,080
However, a beautiful woman,

178
00:09:40,240 --> 00:09:41,570
you like looking at her,

179
00:09:41,880 --> 00:09:43,440
and others do too.

180
00:09:45,640 --> 00:09:46,970
What do you mean by that?

181
00:09:48,120 --> 00:09:49,040
Aren't you men

182
00:09:49,200 --> 00:09:50,040
just the same?

183
00:10:07,440 --> 00:10:08,240
What's wrong?

184
00:10:09,000 --> 00:10:10,930
What's making you so sentimental?

185
00:10:18,480 --> 00:10:19,940
I've been so busy with work

186
00:10:20,840 --> 00:10:24,170
that I've neglected the feelings I should cherish the most.

187
00:10:59,600 --> 00:11:00,120
Master.

188
00:11:00,400 --> 00:11:01,800
The owner said that on the night of the 25th,

189
00:11:01,800 --> 00:11:03,600
he remembers seeing Tian Liang.

190
00:11:03,800 --> 00:11:04,200
Hello.

191
00:11:04,840 --> 00:11:06,970
Do you remember the approximate time?

192
00:11:07,560 --> 00:11:09,320
My shop usually closes at 9:30.

193
00:11:10,280 --> 00:11:12,160
I heard it was quite noisy outside,

194
00:11:12,160 --> 00:11:13,760
so I was going to check it out.

195
00:11:15,560 --> 00:11:16,400
After I went out,

196
00:11:16,400 --> 00:11:17,480
I saw a man

197
00:11:17,600 --> 00:11:19,480
staggering to his feet and leaving,

198
00:11:19,480 --> 00:11:21,210
so I didn't pay much attention.

199
00:11:23,400 --> 00:11:24,040
Was it him?

200
00:11:27,600 --> 00:11:28,440
It was too dark.

201
00:11:28,440 --> 00:11:29,920
I couldn't see his face at all.

202
00:11:29,920 --> 00:11:30,780
But that person

203
00:11:30,920 --> 00:11:32,040
had broad shoulders,

204
00:11:32,040 --> 00:11:33,720
and his build was very similar to this guy's.

205
00:11:33,720 --> 00:11:34,880
Do you remember

206
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:36,730
what the attacker looked like?

207
00:11:37,360 --> 00:11:38,360
I can't remember.

208
00:11:41,480 --> 00:11:41,880
Boss,

209
00:11:42,040 --> 00:11:44,040
