210
00:11:44,280 --> 00:11:45,080
They work,

211
00:11:45,160 --> 00:11:45,640
but

212
00:11:45,760 --> 00:11:48,290
they only cover part of the inside of the shop.

213
00:11:49,880 --> 00:11:50,400
Li,

214
00:11:51,000 --> 00:11:51,720
call Shen Feng over.

215
00:11:51,720 --> 00:11:52,200
Okay.

216
00:11:54,680 --> 00:11:55,280
Thank you.

217
00:11:58,280 --> 00:11:59,080
Captain Shen,

218
00:11:59,280 --> 00:11:59,720
Captain Jiang wants you...

219
00:11:59,720 --> 00:12:00,240
Li,

220
00:12:01,840 --> 00:12:03,240
call Captain Jiang over.

221
00:12:04,280 --> 00:12:04,840
Okay.

222
00:12:16,320 --> 00:12:16,880
Xiaoyun.

223
00:12:18,080 --> 00:12:19,680
You've been drinking again.

224
00:12:19,800 --> 00:12:21,360
What's wrong with a little drink?

225
00:12:21,360 --> 00:12:21,960
Come here.

226
00:12:24,160 --> 00:12:25,890
Who ruins their body like this?

227
00:12:26,200 --> 00:12:26,960
Ruin?

228
00:12:28,360 --> 00:12:29,760
I'm enjoying it.

229
00:12:32,520 --> 00:12:33,580
You go enjoy it too.

230
00:12:33,840 --> 00:12:35,040
Where did the money come from?

231
00:12:35,040 --> 00:12:36,240
Don't worry about it.

232
00:12:37,520 --> 00:12:38,720
I didn't steal or rob.

233
00:12:39,200 --> 00:12:40,730
I earned it fair and square.

234
00:12:41,040 --> 00:12:41,640
Let me go.

235
00:12:42,720 --> 00:12:43,480
Xiaoyun.

236
00:12:44,120 --> 00:12:45,380
You are my girlfriend.

237
00:12:46,560 --> 00:12:47,800
What's wrong with spending time with me?

238
00:12:47,800 --> 00:12:49,330
Luyang, what are you doing?

239
00:12:51,480 --> 00:12:52,010
Xiaoyun.

240
00:12:53,160 --> 00:12:53,690
Xiaoyun.

241
00:13:15,880 --> 00:13:16,740
Captain Jiang.

242
00:13:30,480 --> 00:13:31,120
Auntie,

243
00:13:31,880 --> 00:13:32,610
you're back.

244
00:13:33,640 --> 00:13:34,440
What's wrong?

245
00:13:38,640 --> 00:13:39,700
What's the matter?

246
00:13:39,920 --> 00:13:41,120
I'm not in a good mood.

247
00:13:41,880 --> 00:13:43,480
Why aren't you in a good mood?

248
00:13:44,120 --> 00:13:45,580
Did you fight with Lu Yang?

249
00:13:47,880 --> 00:13:49,160
That kid is really something.

250
00:13:49,160 --> 00:13:49,880
He's all grown up,

251
00:13:49,880 --> 00:13:51,080
but not mature at all.

252
00:13:51,560 --> 00:13:53,090
Alright, it's not worth it.

253
00:13:54,160 --> 00:13:55,090
Go back and rest.

254
00:13:55,320 --> 00:13:55,800
Okay.

255
00:14:02,520 --> 00:14:03,980
Young people nowadays...

256
00:14:10,080 --> 00:14:10,640
Lu Yang.

257
00:14:12,440 --> 00:14:13,900
How could you do this to me?

258
00:14:41,200 --> 00:14:41,730
Drink up.

259
00:14:41,760 --> 00:14:42,160
Okay.

260
00:14:44,880 --> 00:14:46,880
Find me whenever you come here.

261
00:14:47,840 --> 00:14:49,100
We'll get going first.

262
00:14:53,320 --> 00:14:54,360
Yang.

263
00:14:54,520 --> 00:14:56,050
What brings you here today?

264
00:14:56,480 --> 00:14:58,000
Which liquor would you like to order?

265
00:14:58,000 --> 00:14:59,640
Bring the most expensive one.

266
00:14:59,640 --> 00:15:00,040
Okay.

267
00:15:00,800 --> 00:15:02,530
Get the most expensive liquor.

268
00:15:05,640 --> 00:15:06,440
Here, Yang.

269
00:15:28,040 --> 00:15:28,570
Xiaoyun.

270
00:15:30,840 --> 00:15:31,370
Xiaoyun.

271
00:15:31,600 --> 00:15:32,730
Stop being mad at me.

272
00:15:32,760 --> 00:15:33,800
I just bought you

273
00:15:34,640 --> 00:15:35,770
