274
00:15:42,240 --> 00:15:43,900
Xiaoyun, I have a favor to ask.

275
00:15:44,600 --> 00:15:45,280
What is it?

276
00:15:46,760 --> 00:15:48,320
I owe people money.

277
00:15:50,920 --> 00:15:52,080
Two hundred thousand.

278
00:15:52,080 --> 00:15:53,280
How do you owe so much?

279
00:15:54,000 --> 00:15:55,880
I originally borrowed 50 or 60 thousand.

280
00:15:55,880 --> 00:15:57,160
Who knew their campus loans

281
00:15:57,160 --> 00:15:59,200
