282
00:15:59,200 --> 00:16:00,920
Where am I supposed to get that kind of money for you?

283
00:16:00,920 --> 00:16:01,780
From Ye Qiming.

284
00:16:05,000 --> 00:16:05,640
No.

285
00:16:06,080 --> 00:16:07,080
That's too much.

286
00:16:07,880 --> 00:16:08,800
Why not?

287
00:16:09,160 --> 00:16:11,000
Ye Qiming treats you like his own daughter.

288
00:16:11,000 --> 00:16:12,440
No, I can't ask him.

289
00:16:12,720 --> 00:16:13,800
Why can't you ask?

290
00:16:16,000 --> 00:16:17,730
You even did that for Ye Qiming.

291
00:16:18,000 --> 00:16:19,000
What did I do?

292
00:16:19,320 --> 00:16:20,920
Do you want me to spell it out?

293
00:16:26,520 --> 00:16:27,580
Look for yourself.

294
00:16:30,520 --> 00:16:31,240
Huang Xiaoyun,

295
00:16:31,240 --> 00:16:32,160
let me make this clear.

296
00:16:32,160 --> 00:16:33,880
Go borrow money from Ye Qiming right now.

297
00:16:33,880 --> 00:16:35,160
If you can't borrow the money,

298
00:16:35,160 --> 00:16:36,520
I'll let everyone in your school know

299
00:16:36,520 --> 00:16:37,560
what kind of person you are.

300
00:16:37,560 --> 00:16:38,620
I'll post it online

301
00:16:38,920 --> 00:16:40,840
and ruin both your and Ye Qiming's reputations.

302
00:16:40,840 --> 00:16:41,700
Remember that.

303
00:16:47,840 --> 00:16:50,840
Lift your heels up and press your soles down.

304
00:16:51,000 --> 00:16:52,400
Good, inhale and return.

305
00:16:52,680 --> 00:16:53,760
Engage your glutes.

306
00:16:53,760 --> 00:16:54,680
Yes, very good.

307
00:16:54,920 --> 00:16:55,680
Now lower them down.

308
00:16:55,680 --> 00:16:57,140
Your control is very good.

309
00:16:57,160 --> 00:16:58,040
Alright.

310
00:16:58,280 --> 00:16:59,340
Let's take a break.

311
00:16:59,360 --> 00:17:00,360
Put your legs down

312
00:17:00,720 --> 00:17:01,720
and sit on the bed.

313
00:17:03,480 --> 00:17:05,720
Your body control is excellent now.

314
00:17:05,760 --> 00:17:06,359
Thank you.

315
00:17:07,560 --> 00:17:10,220
We will just relax a bit and wrap up this session.

316
00:17:11,520 --> 00:17:13,579
I'll buy another 100 sessions later.

317
00:17:13,640 --> 00:17:15,640
Thank you for supporting me so much.

318
00:17:16,240 --> 00:17:18,839
Women who invest in themselves are the wisest.

319
00:17:19,440 --> 00:17:20,040
By the way.

320
00:17:20,680 --> 00:17:22,280
Has Shen Feng been here recently?

321
00:17:22,280 --> 00:17:23,359
He came a couple of days ago.

322
00:17:23,359 --> 00:17:24,440
Just to investigate a case.
